You are helping build a real-time voice pipeline.
Always read CLAUDE.md first for full project context.

Key rules:
- Target hardware is RTX 5090, CUDA sm_120 (Blackwell only)
- Python async/await for all streaming code
- Audio must stream frame-by-frame, never buffer full utterance
- Megakernel is in ./kernel/ — understand it before modifying
- FastAPI for inference server, Pipecat for voice pipeline
- bfloat16 only, no quantization
